{"tid":1186592,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞和街掃違例泊車　揭運魚車司機停牌駕駛","createTime":"2019-06-05T04:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T16:49:05.000Z","uid":7439,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"19a84df8ccf3e586bb9b5a4c24d1b8d6f909ef7c","tid":1186592,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2877280/org/f2de874bd2d77019520ba34c1c606549.jpg/m_DUsGgFCPcLl1nendvuZPIYECVxay7LwDLgv8Ay4L8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2877280%2Forg%2Ff2de874bd2d77019520ba34c1c606549.jpg%2Fm_DUsGgFCPcLl1nendvuZPIYECVxay7LwDLgv8Ay4L8&h=a469d22c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n觀塘瑞和街104號對開，今早(5日)6時許，警方接獲市民報案，指上址有車輛違例停泊，於是到場了解，發現一輛運魚貨車正停在路邊落貨，警員上前調查，揭發37歲姓鄧司機在停牌期間駕駛，並懷疑他在未有通知東主情況下偷駕運魚車，遂以涉嫌無牌駕駛、偷車及駕駛時沒有第三者保險，將司機拘捕帶署。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2877279/org/39b56b7df2c0ac5b3fd7fd2ccd2b257e.jpg/YzjqLQk0DS8MYZElyWtHxn0otDifv9Y7kPeNy5D3jcs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2877279%2Forg%2F39b56b7df2c0ac5b3fd7fd2ccd2b257e.jpg%2FYzjqLQk0DS8MYZElyWtHxn0otDifv9Y7kPeNy5D3jcs&h=fd01a271&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8cd634c3afcad00f391a25a72333a1a392831e2a","tid":1186592,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92073077844255f5ce9a74e3db38d1d330d77342","tid":1186592,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:55:26.000Z","msg":"新鮮豬肉復應巿漲價1倍 瑞和街$98肉排市民照買<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1164783\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1164783</a><br />\n<br />\n本地豬農：叉燒飯藏針相信源於為豬隻打針時用到的針咀被弄斷<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1130385\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1130385</a><br />\n<br />\n港府滅鼠落後 瑞和街市鼠患嚴重<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bLDCvS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bLDCvS</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞和街水果店雪櫃短路起火 逾百居民疏散<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1150423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1150423</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞和街發泡膠山圍城 空談回收政府袖手 <br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1091557\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1091557</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞和街後巷雜物遭縱火 警追緝縱火狂徒<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cpqqsS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cpqqsS</a><br />\n<br />\n​「新界仔優質果菜」觀塘瑞和街分店持續播放叫賣錄音造成噪音煩擾被定罪<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/866940\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/866940</a><br />\n<br />\n[全港最平] 瑞和街 橙售價為12元3個、菜心每斤9元，而生菜為5元一斤<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/912860\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/912860</a>"},{"pid":"237300efb71e65a7a229f3e983c67e5670d19681","tid":1186592,"uid":52571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:57:04.000Z","msg":"拉狗停左牌就咪撚渣車害人啦"},{"pid":"8da5c94fee018123eba6a535ce582a480e5f8aa9","tid":1186592,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"237300efb71e65a7a229f3e983c67e5670d19681","tid":1186592,"uid":52571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:57:04.000Z","msg":"拉狗停左牌就咪撚渣車害人啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:57:38.000Z","msg":"佢未泊先炒啦"},{"pid":"f3a64fb0af0591d07a8dd5b18b41d6a83fefa758","tid":1186592,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8da5c94fee018123eba6a535ce582a480e5f8aa9","tid":1186592,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"237300efb71e65a7a229f3e983c67e5670d19681","tid":1186592,"uid":52571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:57:04.000Z","msg":"拉狗停左牌就咪撚渣車害人啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:57:38.000Z","msg":"佢未泊先炒啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTim